  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为Module 14画一个软删除场景的时序图，核心角色有三个：临床工程师、Azure备份保管库，还有工作负载VM。标题我想定为「Module 14 – Soft Delete (CloudNative_Serverless)」，这样能对应上我们云原生无服务器的技术栈。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Clinical Engineer",
        "Azure Backup Vault",
        "Workload VM",
        "title",
        "CloudNative_Serverless"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，三个参与者已经记下了。关于命名，Clinical Engineer我简写成ClinEng，Azure Backup Vault简写为Azure，Workload VM简写为Workload，这样箭头标注会更清晰。软删除的流程具体怎么触发？是从临床工程师配置策略开始吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ClinEng",
        "Azure",
        "Workload"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，第一步是临床工程师向Azure备份保管库配置备份策略。然后Azure会主动触发工作负载VM的快照备份作业，这是一个异步触发过程。接着工作负载VM把恢复点数据回传给Azure。最后临床工程师还要验证恢复点和报告，确保备份成功。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Configure policy",
        "Trigger snapshot/backup job",
        "Send recovery point",
        "Validate recovery point & reports"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我梳理一下流程：ClinEng到Azure是配置策略的同步调用；Azure到Workload是触发备份作业的异步消息，用虚线箭头；Workload返回恢复点到Azure也是虚线；最后ClinEng再到Azure验证恢复点。这样理解对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ClinEng-Azure",
        "Azure--Workload",
        "Workload--Azure"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，触发和发送恢复点都是异步的，用虚线。配置策略和验证是同步操作，用实线。另外注意Workload返回给Azure的是recovery point，不是完整备份数据，这样表述更准确。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "recovery point",
        "snapshot/backup job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，时序图已绘制完成。三个参与者纵向排列，ClinEng在最左，Azure居中，Workload在右。四条消息按时间顺序从上到下：配置策略、触发作业、发送恢复点、验证报告。标题和CloudNative_Serverless的标注也都加上了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "Module 14 – Soft Delete",
        "CloudNative_Serverless",
        "sequenceDiagram"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我再看一眼，触发作业那一步，箭头方向确认是从Azure指向Workload吧？是Azure主动调用Workload的备份接口，而不是Workload轮询Azure。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Azure--Workload",
        "Trigger snapshot/backup job"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，箭头方向是Azure指向Workload，表示Azure主动触发。整个流程闭环了：工程师配置→Azure调度→Workload执行→数据返回→工程师验证。符合软删除场景下备份策略的完整生命周期。",
